ðŸ”„ 4. THE PROJECT FLOW (The Big Picture)

1.  **Login/Signup**: You give your details -> Server checks them -> Server gives you a "Digital ID Card" (JWT).
2.  **Generate Image**: You type a prompt -> Frontend checks your credits -> Server asks the AI (ClipDrop) to draw it -> Image is shown with a fade-in animation.
3.  **Refilling Credits**: You choose a plan -> Pay through the Razorpay popup -> Server adds credits to your account.

